{"tid":1421792,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民間記者會其實好有用","createTime":"2019-08-06T08:56:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T09:56:19.000Z","uid":80396,"like":107,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e229cf9e9a59132a689431ad1cdf7ee8553d5a81","tid":1421792,"uid":80396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:56:36.000Z","msg":"點解要遊行<br />\n點解要示威<br />\n點解要文宣<br />\n因為要政府聽到我地既聲音，要市民理解我地既表達<br />\n但而家個遊戲玩法係只有政府可以開正式記者會，單方面發佈消息任人魚肉。我地只可以靠文宣去發聲。<br />\n<br />\n今日我地既民間記者會，將會完全改變遊戲玩法，我地既聲音可以光明正大打入每家每戶，可以正正式式大把大把車落政府！<br />\n<br />\n筆比劍更利，希望大家可以支持民間記者會，效果相信會係意想不到<br />\n<br />\n其待下場記者會可以大把大把車落去<br />\n<br />\n各有各做 兄弟爬山<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"b4f3b1f6af020983919062195251b745fdaf6092","tid":1421792,"uid":129120,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:57:37.000Z","msg":"不割席！"},{"pid":"c6a6527cd57e4ffc6ea7f78c07e2c86111ce4978","tid":1421792,"uid":277702,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:58:37.000Z","msg":"真係冇得頂，呢頭講，嗰頭就做咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真心令我覺得香港係有未來㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"929504a657ccece01da0fadb3acea4f2299437ef","tid":1421792,"uid":80396,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:59:05.000Z","msg":"下一場會，應該需要大量狗暴片，需要剪接高手巴打。<br />\n黎！佢地夠膽剪到我地係暴徒，我地都可以揭露真相！"},{"pid":"019799214cea79d6945910432ed45953722f2edd","tid":1421792,"uid":80396,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:00:57.000Z","msg":"大家諗一諗！真心<br />\n政府求其一個記者會講兩句，已經可以分化成個社會，打到前線變暴徒<br />\n知唔知我地要用幾多時間幾多文宣，先可以同大眾解釋清楚<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">記者會既作用就係呢度！</span>"},{"pid":"82aac2ba23b1692c70e024b86dd6241244035c53","tid":1421792,"uid":19528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:01:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f1c4a87e52cbb420002b45c902410b403598de73","tid":1421792,"uid":19528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:02:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e1489f4ce3670a421d9cf3f880e9856f82fd297","tid":1421792,"uid":65858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:02:48.000Z","msg":"請必須要回應黑警嘅每一個大話"},{"pid":"3aefe417ff76539eebf1039f07ef3a21d37b8670","tid":1421792,"uid":80396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e1489f4ce3670a421d9cf3f880e9856f82fd297","tid":1421792,"uid":65858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:02:48.000Z","msg":"請必須要回應黑警嘅每一個大話"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:04:19.000Z","msg":"正確！雖然今日個記者會有點柒！<br />\n但我相信佢地會進步，會一步步成長！<br />\n記者會將會係好大既武器！"},{"pid":"934beb8bacbe1be0bd1995a073ba90a1ffebc6aa","tid":1421792,"uid":132175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:04:48.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"b551891ad38b5c568130cb67d33cb68eca86ec66","tid":1421792,"uid":194133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3aefe417ff76539eebf1039f07ef3a21d37b8670","tid":1421792,"uid":80396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e1489f4ce3670a421d9cf3f880e9856f82fd297","tid":1421792,"uid":65858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:02:48.000Z","msg":"請必須要回應黑警嘅每一個大話"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:04:19.000Z","msg":"正確！雖然今日個記者會有點柒！<br />\n但我相信佢地會進步，會一步步成長！<br />\n記者會將會係好大既武器！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:06:43.000Z","msg":"都唔算柒 尤其個女仔答得有紋有路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbeabdd31599da8a679780aa58bc126d97a42a2f","tid":1421792,"uid":19528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:07:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"39eb815101cec7bd2092d7328e37dc947665cd49","tid":1421792,"uid":267395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:08:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8b1d76334f577c3ddea49f3ced71a37a5fe55552","tid":1421792,"uid":69866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco